            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Orient</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">：面向，对着</span></span></li>

                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Programming</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">：编程。</span></span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">在我们的程序中，经常存在一些系统性的需求，比如权限校验、日志记录、统计等，这些代码会散落穿插在各个业务逻辑中，非常冗余且不利于维护</span></span></span>
    </li>
</ul>

<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">中重要的三个要素：</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Aspect</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Pointcut , Advice.
            </span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">这个概念的理解是：</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                        style="color:#24292e">Advice</span></span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                        style="color:#24292e">的时间</span></span></strong></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">切入，也就是权限校验等非业务操作在哪些业务代码中执行。</span></span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                        style="color:#24292e">Pointcut</span></span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                        style="color:#24292e">的位置</span></span></strong></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                    style="color:black">切入，是业务代码执行前还是执行后。</span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">切入后</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                        style="color:#24292e">执行</span></span></strong></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><strong><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                        style="color:#24292e">Aspect</span></span></strong></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">，比如做权限校验、日志记录等</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是一个动态的思想。
                在程序运行期间，创建代理（</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ServcieProxy</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">），使用代理执行方法时，增加切面的功能。这个代理对象是存在内存中的。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 40px;"><img
        src="data:image/png;base64,"
        style="height:638px; width:779px"></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">你要给某些方法 增加相同的一些功能。
                源代码不能改。 给业务方法增加非业务功能，也可以使用</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="color:#24292e"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></strong><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">作用</span></strong></span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">让切面功能复用</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">让开发人员专注业务逻辑。
                提高开发效率</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">实现业务功能和其他非业务功能解耦合。</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">给存在的业务方法，
                增加功能，不用修改原来的代码</span></span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:13.5pt"><span style="color:#24292e"><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></strong><strong><span
                    style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的实现</span></strong></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-left:36px"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#24292e"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">使用框架实现</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。 实现</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的框架有很多。 有名的两个</span></span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
    <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spr</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ing </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">：</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架实现</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">思想中的部分功能。</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架实现</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的操作比较繁琐，比重。</span></span>
    </li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Asp</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ectj </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">：
                独立的框架，专门是</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AOP</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。 属于</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Eclipse</span></span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><span
                style="color:#24292e"><strong>原理</strong></span></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring aop
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是基于代理的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> aop </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">框架。这意味着</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">要实现目标对象的各个方面</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">它将创建该对象的代理。使用以下两种方法之一实现</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">:</span></span>
        <ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
            <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">JDK
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">动态代理 ——</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring AOP
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的首选方式。只要目标对象实现甚至一个接口</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">就会使用</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> JDK
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">动态代理；</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">CGLIB
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">代理 —— 如果目标对象没有实现接口</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">则可以使用</span></span><span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> CGLIB
                    </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">代理。</span></span></li>
        </ol>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;AspectJ
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在运行时不做任何事情</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">因为类是直接用方面进行编译的。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">与</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring AOP </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">不同</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">它不需要任何设计模式。为了编织代码的各个方面</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">它引入了称为</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> AspectJ </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">编译器</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (ajc) </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的编译器</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">通过它编译我们的程序</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">然后通过提供一个小型</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (100K) </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">运行时库来运行它</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><strong>简易性</strong></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring AOP
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">显然更简单</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">因为它不会在我们的构建过程中引入任何额外的编译器或织入。它使用运行时编织</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">因此它与我们通常的构建过程无缝集成。虽然它看起来很简单</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">但它只适用于由</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">管理的</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> bean</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">使用</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> AspectJ, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">我们需要引入</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> AspectJ </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">编译器</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (ajc) </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">并重新打包所有的库</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">除非我们切换到编译后或加载时间的织入</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">)</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">。</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">当然</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这比前者更复杂</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">因为它引入了</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> AspectJ Java </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">工具</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">包括编译器</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (ajc)</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、调试器</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (ajdb)</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、文档生成器</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (ajdoc)</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">、程序结构浏览器</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> (ajbrowser)), </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">我们需要将它们与我们的</span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> IDE </span><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">或生成工具。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;"><strong>性能</strong></span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">就性能而言</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">编译时织入比运行时织入快得多。</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Spring AOP
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是基于代理的框架</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">因此在应用程序启动时会创建代理。另外</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">每个方面还有一些方法调用</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">这会对性能产生负面影响。</span></span>
    </li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">AspectJ </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">在应用程序执行之前将这些方面编织到主代码中</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">因此没有额外的运行时开销</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">与</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring AOP </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">不同。</span></span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">基于这些原因</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">, </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">基准表明</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> AspectJ </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的速度几乎比</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Spring AOP </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">快</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">8</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">到</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">35</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">倍</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
